pulltitle: Use v2 search endpoint for operator dashboard (bug 1136460)
pullsbody:
https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1136460

**We weren't really using the endpoint to search for non-public apps**. This endpoint only exists in v2 on zamboni, but this didn't 404 because the v1 search endpoint regexp in zamboni didn't end with a `$`, so we were really querying the public search endpoint... This will be fixed by https://github.com/mozilla/zamboni/pull/2958
pull_repo_desc: Operator dashboard for the Firefox Marketplace
pull_commit_message:
Use v2 search endpoint for operator dashboard (bug 1136460)

We weren't really using the endpoint to search for non-public apps.
This endpoint only exists in v2 on zamboni, but this didn't 404
because the search endpoint regexp in zamboni didn't end with a '$',
so we were really querying the public search endpoint... This will
be fixed by https://github.com/mozilla/zamboni/pull/2958
